            "last_activity_date": 1415303287,
            "creation_date": 1415303287,
            "body": "<p>I solved the problem changing in gradle<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>compile 'com.android.support:appcompat-v7:21.0.0'\ncompile 'com.android.support:support-v4:21.0.0'\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>to<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>compile 'com.android.support:appcompat-v7:19.0.0'\ncompile 'com.android.support:support-v4:19.0.0'\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>and compile / target sdk to 19<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 26788138,
            "question_id": 26718480
        },
